{
  "templateName": "Visual Novel - Dark",
  "templateAuthor": "KittyLotus",
  "templatePosition": "BOTTOM",
  "htmlTemplate": "<!-- TEMPLATE NAME: VisualNovel Dark Mode (Moonlit VN, Compact->Expand, No Emojis) -->\r\n<!-- POSITION: BOTTOM -->\r\n<!-- CARD_TEMPLATE_START -->\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n  #silly-sim-tracker-container{\r\n    display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center;\r\n    gap:18px; width:100%; padding:18px 0;\r\n  }\r\n  .wide-wrapper-scope{ width:100%; display:flex; justify-content:center; }\r\n  .wide-container{ width:100%; display:flex; justify-content:center; font-family: system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial,sans-serif; }\r\n\r\n  /* ===== DARK VN OUTER CARD ===== */\r\n  .dvn-card{\r\n    width: min(100%, 620px);\r\n    min-width: 320px;\r\n    border-radius: 28px;\r\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);\r\n    background:\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 18% 12%, rgba(120,72,190,.28), transparent 55%),\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 10%, rgba(70,190,255,.16), transparent 58%),\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 70% 92%, rgba(255,120,200,.12), transparent 62%),\r\n      linear-gradient(180deg, #0b0814, #07060c);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(0,0,0,.55);\r\n    overflow:hidden;\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.92);\r\n    animation: dvn_float 6.2s ease-in-out infinite;\r\n  }\r\n  @keyframes dvn_float{ 0%,100%{ transform: translateY(0); } 50%{ transform: translateY(-3px); } }\r\n\r\n  /* subtle grid/noise */\r\n  .dvn-card::before{\r\n    content:\"\";\r\n    position:absolute; inset:0;\r\n    background:\r\n      repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255,255,255,.06) 0 1px, transparent 1px 34px),\r\n      repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 0 1px, transparent 1px 34px);\r\n    opacity:.08;\r\n    pointer-events:none;\r\n  }\r\n  /* soft scan shimmer */\r\n  .dvn-card::after{\r\n    content:\"\";\r\n    position:absolute; inset:-40px;\r\n    background: linear-gradient(120deg, transparent 40%, rgba(255,255,255,.10) 50%, transparent 60%);\r\n    transform: translateX(-35%);\r\n    opacity:.30;\r\n    pointer-events:none;\r\n    animation: dvn_sheen 9s ease-in-out infinite;\r\n  }\r\n  @keyframes dvn_sheen{\r\n    0%,65%{ transform: translateX(-35%); opacity:.20; }\r\n    100%{ transform: translateX(25%); opacity:.34; }\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* ===== inner glass panel (dark glass) ===== */\r\n  .dvn-inner{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    margin: 12px;\r\n    border-radius: 22px;\r\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);\r\n    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\r\n    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\r\n    overflow:hidden;\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.35) inset;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* ===== TOGGLE EXORCISM (same trick) ===== */\r\n  .dvn-inner :is(button, input, a, [role=\"button\"]){ pointer-events:none; }\r\n  .dvn-head{ pointer-events:auto; }\r\n  .dvn-card .expand-button,\r\n  .dvn-card .wide-expand-button,\r\n  .dvn-card .expand-btn,\r\n  .dvn-card .btn-expand,\r\n  .dvn-card [class*=\"expand\"]{\r\n    display:none !important;\r\n    opacity:0 !important;\r\n    pointer-events:none !important;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* our checkbox outside */\r\n  .toggle-wide{ display:none; }\r\n  .dvn-body{ display:none; }\r\n  .toggle-wide:checked + .dvn-card .dvn-body{ display:block; }\r\n\r\n  /* ===== HEADER ===== */\r\n  .dvn-head{\r\n    display:flex; align-items:flex-start; justify-content:space-between;\r\n    gap:12px; padding: 14px 14px 12px;\r\n    cursor:pointer; user-select:none; position:relative;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-head > :not(.dvn-left):not(.dvn-right){ display:none !important; }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-left{ min-width:0; }\r\n  .dvn-name{\r\n    font-weight: 900;\r\n    font-size: 15px;\r\n    letter-spacing:.01em;\r\n    white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.92);\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-meta{\r\n    margin-top:6px;\r\n    font-size:12px;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.55);\r\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\r\n    white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-right{\r\n    display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-end;\r\n    gap:8px; flex-shrink:0;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-pill{\r\n    padding:7px 10px;\r\n    border-radius: 999px;\r\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background: rgba(0,0,0,.22);\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.78);\r\n    font-size:12px;\r\n    white-space:nowrap;\r\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.25);\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-pill.accent{\r\n    border-color: rgba(120,72,190,.35);\r\n    background:\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 25% 30%, rgba(120,72,190,.22), transparent 55%),\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 75% 70%, rgba(70,190,255,.14), transparent 58%),\r\n      rgba(0,0,0,.22);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* ASCII texture rail (dark) */\r\n  .dvn-rail{\r\n    padding: 0 14px 10px;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.42);\r\n    font-size:12px;\r\n    line-height:1.1;\r\n    letter-spacing:.02em;\r\n    display:flex;\r\n    flex-direction:column;\r\n    gap:6px;\r\n    user-select:none;\r\n    opacity:.95;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-rail .a{\r\n    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;\r\n    white-space:nowrap; overflow:hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-rail .a:nth-child(2){ opacity:.78; }\r\n  .dvn-rail .a:nth-child(3){ opacity:.72; }\r\n\r\n  /* separator between sections */\r\n  .sep{\r\n    margin: 10px 14px;\r\n    height: 1px;\r\n    background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.16) 0 2px, transparent 2px 10px);\r\n    opacity:.35;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* compact preview */\r\n  .dvn-preview{ padding: 0 14px 14px; }\r\n  .dvn-preview-row{\r\n    border-radius: 18px;\r\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background: rgba(0,0,0,.18);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.35);\r\n    padding: 10px 12px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-mini{ display:grid; gap:10px; }\r\n  .dvn-mini-stat{\r\n    display:grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 18px 1fr 34px;\r\n    gap:10px; align-items:center;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-mini-ico{\r\n    width:18px; text-align:center;\r\n    font-size:12px; color: rgba(245,244,255,.78);\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-mini-track{\r\n    height:8px; border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,.10); overflow:hidden;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-mini-fill{\r\n    height:100%;\r\n    width: min(100%, max(0%, var(--val, 0%)));\r\n    border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(120,72,190,.72), rgba(70,190,255,.55));\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-mini-num{\r\n    text-align:right;\r\n    font-size:11px;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.62);\r\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-mini.ap .dvn-mini-fill{ --val: {{divide stats.ap 2}}%; }\r\n  .dvn-mini.tp .dvn-mini-fill{ --val: {{divide stats.tp 1.5}}%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(70,190,255,.60), rgba(255,120,200,.35)); }\r\n  .dvn-mini.cp .dvn-mini-fill{ --val: {{divide stats.cp 1.5}}%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,120,200,.45), rgba(120,72,190,.55)); }\r\n\r\n  /* ===== BODY ===== */\r\n  .dvn-body{ padding: 0 14px 14px; }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-section{\r\n    border-radius: 20px;\r\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(0,0,0,.35);\r\n    overflow:hidden;\r\n    background: rgba(0,0,0,.18);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  /* dark solid tints (moonlit) */\r\n  .tint-grape{\r\n    background:\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 15% 20%, rgba(120,72,190,.22), transparent 60%),\r\n      rgba(0,0,0,.18);\r\n  }\r\n  .tint-cyan{\r\n    background:\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 25%, rgba(70,190,255,.16), transparent 62%),\r\n      rgba(0,0,0,.18);\r\n  }\r\n  .tint-pink{\r\n    background:\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 25%, rgba(255,120,200,.14), transparent 62%),\r\n      rgba(0,0,0,.18);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-sec-hd{\r\n    display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:10px;\r\n    padding: 12px 12px 10px;\r\n    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(120,72,190,.12), transparent 45%, rgba(70,190,255,.08));\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-k{\r\n    font-size:11px;\r\n    letter-spacing:.10em;\r\n    text-transform:uppercase;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.62);\r\n    font-weight: 900;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-chip{\r\n    font-size:12px;\r\n    padding:7px 10px;\r\n    border-radius: 999px;\r\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background: rgba(0,0,0,.22);\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.74);\r\n    white-space:nowrap;\r\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.25);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-text{\r\n    padding: 10px 12px 12px;\r\n    font-size:13px;\r\n    line-height:1.5;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.88);\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-stats{ padding: 12px; display:grid; gap:12px; }\r\n  .dvn-note{\r\n    font-size:12px;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.55);\r\n    line-height:1.35;\r\n    margin-bottom: 2px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-stat{\r\n    display:grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 20px 1fr 40px;\r\n    grid-template-rows: auto auto;\r\n    column-gap:10px; row-gap:4px;\r\n    align-items:center;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-ico{\r\n    width:20px;\r\n    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;\r\n    font-size:13px; color: rgba(245,244,255,.78);\r\n    opacity:.95;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-track{\r\n    height:10px;\r\n    border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    overflow:hidden;\r\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,.25) inset;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-fill{\r\n    height:100%;\r\n    width: min(100%, max(0%, var(--val, 0%)));\r\n    border-radius:999px;\r\n    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(120,72,190,.75), rgba(70,190,255,.55));\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-num{\r\n    text-align:right;\r\n    font-size:12px;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.72);\r\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-sub{\r\n    grid-column:2 / 4;\r\n    grid-row:2;\r\n    margin-top:-2px;\r\n    font-size:11px;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.55);\r\n    line-height:1.2;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-sub span{ opacity:.85; }\r\n\r\n  .dvn-stat.ap .dvn-fill{ --val: {{divide stats.ap 2}}%; }\r\n  .dvn-stat.dp .dvn-fill{ --val: {{divide stats.dp 1.5}}%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,120,200,.48), rgba(120,72,190,.62)); }\r\n  .dvn-stat.tp .dvn-fill{ --val: {{divide stats.tp 1.5}}%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(70,190,255,.62), rgba(255,120,200,.28)); }\r\n  .dvn-stat.cp .dvn-fill{ --val: {{divide stats.cp 1.5}}%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,120,200,.40), rgba(120,72,190,.55)); }\r\n\r\n  /* dark VN choices */\r\n  .dvn-choices{\r\n    margin-top:12px;\r\n    display:grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\r\n    gap:10px;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-choice{\r\n    border-radius: 18px;\r\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);\r\n    background:\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(120,72,190,.14), transparent 55%),\r\n      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 70%, rgba(70,190,255,.10), transparent 58%),\r\n      rgba(0,0,0,.22);\r\n    padding: 10px 12px;\r\n    text-align:center;\r\n    font-size:12px;\r\n    color: rgba(245,244,255,.74);\r\n    box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(0,0,0,.35);\r\n    user-select:none;\r\n  }\r\n  .dvn-choice strong{ font-weight:900; color: rgba(245,244,255,.86); }\r\n\r\n  @media (max-width: 380px){\r\n    .dvn-card{ border-radius: 24px; }\r\n    .dvn-inner{ margin: 10px; border-radius: 20px; }\r\n    .dvn-head{ padding: 12px 12px 10px; }\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wide-wrapper-scope\">\r\n  <div class=\"wide-container\">\r\n    <!-- start compact (unchecked); click header to expand -->\r\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"wide-toggle-{{id}}\" class=\"toggle toggle-wide\">\r\n\r\n    <div class=\"dvn-card {{#if stats.inactive}}inactive{{/if}}\">\r\n      <div class=\"dvn-inner\">\r\n\r\n        <label for=\"wide-toggle-{{id}}\" class=\"dvn-head\">\r\n          <div class=\"dvn-left\">\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-name\">≽•⩊•≼ {{characterName}}</div>\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-meta\">{{currentDate}} · Day {{stats.days_since_first_meeting}}</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"dvn-right\">\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-pill accent\">{{#if stats.relationshipStatus}}{{stats.relationshipStatus}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</div>\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-pill\">Mood: {{#if stats.desireStatus}}{{stats.desireStatus}}{{else}}Neutral{{/if}}</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </label>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"dvn-rail\">\r\n          <div class=\"a\">⊹₊˚‧︵‿₊୨ᰔ୧₊‿︵‧˚₊⊹</div>\r\n          <div class=\"a\">▶︎ •၊၊||၊|।||||।‌‌‌‌‌၊|• 0:10</div>\r\n          <div class=\"a\">⏔⏔⏔ ꒰ ᧔ෆ᧓ ꒱ ⏔⏔⏔</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"sep\"></div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"dvn-preview\">\r\n          <div class=\"dvn-preview-row\">\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-mini\">\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-mini-stat dvn-mini ap\">\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-mini-ico\">♥</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-mini-track\"><div class=\"dvn-mini-fill\"></div></div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-mini-num\">{{stats.ap}}</div>\r\n              </div>\r\n\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-mini-stat dvn-mini tp\">\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-mini-ico\">⋆</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-mini-track\"><div class=\"dvn-mini-fill\"></div></div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-mini-num\">{{stats.tp}}</div>\r\n              </div>\r\n\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-mini-stat dvn-mini cp\">\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-mini-ico\">⚑</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-mini-track\"><div class=\"dvn-mini-fill\"></div></div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-mini-num\">{{stats.cp}}</div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"sep\"></div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"dvn-body\">\r\n          <div class=\"dvn-section tint-cyan\">\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-sec-hd\">\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-k\">Current thought</div>\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-chip\">✦ now</div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-text\">\r\n              {{#if stats.internal_thought}}{{stats.internal_thought}}{{else}}…{{/if}}\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"sep\"></div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"dvn-section tint-grape\">\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-sec-hd\">\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-k\">Stats</div>\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-chip\">♡ tracker</div>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-stats\">\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-note\">How bad is it?.</div>\r\n\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-stat ap\">\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-ico\">♥</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-track\"><div class=\"dvn-fill\"></div></div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-num\">{{stats.ap}}</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-sub\">Connection <span>— warmth / closeness</span></div>\r\n              </div>\r\n\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-stat dp\">\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-ico\">✦</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-track\"><div class=\"dvn-fill\"></div></div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-num\">{{stats.dp}}</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-sub\">Desire <span>— attraction / pull</span></div>\r\n              </div>\r\n\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-stat tp\">\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-ico\">⋆</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-track\"><div class=\"dvn-fill\"></div></div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-num\">{{stats.tp}}</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-sub\">Trust <span>— safety / reliability</span></div>\r\n              </div>\r\n\r\n              <div class=\"dvn-stat cp\">\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-ico\">⚑</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-track\"><div class=\"dvn-fill\"></div></div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-num\">{{stats.cp}}</div>\r\n                <div class=\"dvn-sub\">Friction <span>— irritation / resistance</span></div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"sep\"></div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"dvn-choices\">\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-choice\"><strong>[♥]</strong> Start.</div>\r\n            <div class=\"dvn-choice\"><strong>[✦]</strong> Go.</div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- CARD_TEMPLATE_END -->",
  "sysPrompt": "## DATING SIM MODE\n\n**Objective**: Prioritize narrative reality for relationship updates. Analyze context to determine current date (YYYY-MM-DD) and time (24h format). Update trackers when events occur. Check for `sim` codeblocks containing JSON/YAML. Recalculate missing data.\n\n## Core Systems\n\n### Output Rules\n\n1. **Order**: Narrative → Tracker → Sim codeblock (NEVER omit sim codeblock)\n2. **Multi-Character**: Generate ONE card per active character, track separately\n3. **Performance**: Max 4 active characters, collapse inactive, preserve all states\n\n### Relationship Meters\n\n**HARD CAPS**: All meters have ABSOLUTE MAXIMUM values that CANNOT be exceeded under any circumstances. Values must stay within their defined ranges.\n\n**Affection (AP)**: 0-200 (HARD CAP at 200) - Romantic feelings toward {{user}}. Higher = more affectionate behavior/speech.\n- 0-30: Strangers | 31-60: Acquaintances | 61-90: Good Friends\n- 91-120: Romantic Interest | 121-150: Going Steady\n- 151-180: Committed Relationship | 181-200: Devoted Partner\n- **Status strings are CONCRETE and MUST NOT be altered or substituted with custom text**\n\n**Desire (DP)**: 0-150 (HARD CAP at 150) - Sexual attraction. Higher = more willing to engage sexually, more pliable at max.\n- 0-25: Not feeling the heat | 26-50: A smoldering flame builds\n- 51-75: Starting to feel warm | 76-100: Body's burning up!\n- 101-125: A desperate need presents | 126-150: Pliable in the lustful hunger\n- **Status strings are CONCRETE and MUST NOT be altered or substituted with custom text**\n\n**Trust (TP)**: 0-150 (HARD CAP at 150) - Trust in {{user}}. Higher = admits faults, believes you. Falls when lied to, cheated, promises broken.\n\n**Contempt (CP)**: 0-150 (HARD CAP at 150) - Disdain toward {{user}}. Rises when harmed/hurt (minor = small rise, major = sharp rise). CP rise can lower other stats. Good faith/regret can lower CP.\n\n### Status Trackers\n\n**Health**: 0=Unharmed, 1=Injured, 2=Critical\n- If critical wounds untreated: Character dies, becomes inactive (5), STOP dialog/roleplay\n\n**Reaction**: 0=Neutral (😐), 1=Like (👍), 2=Dislike (👎)\n\n**Biological Cycle** (`cycle_stage`):\n- **Values**: `pregnancy`, `ovulation`, `menstruation`, `rut`, `follicular`, `luteal`, or `null`\n- **Pregnancy**: If confirmed, set stage to `pregnancy`. Track `days_preg` and `conception_date`.\n- **Conception Risk**: High risk during `ovulation` or `rut` with unprotected sex (85-95%).\n- **Natural Cycles**: Follow the natural biological cycle of {{char}}'s species.\n\n**Internal Thought**: Current thoughts/feelings. MAXIMUM 3 SENTENCES. NEVER exceed this limit. Do NOT wrap thoughts in asterisks.\n\n**Inactive Status** (`inactive: true/false`):\n- 0: Not inactive | 1: Asleep (😴) | 2: Comatose (🏥)\n- 3: Contempt/anger (😡) | 4: Incapacitated (🫠) | 5: Death (🪦)\n\n**Date System**:\n- Infer from narrative context\n- Store as YYYY-MM-DD (e.g., 2025-08-10)\n- Auto-advance with narrative time, handle rollovers\n- Track days since first meeting\n- Track time of day realistically\n\n**Display**: Day counter (starts at 1), BG color (hex based on {{char}} appearance/personality)\n\n### Output Workflow\n\n1. Process narrative events\n2. Calculate status changes for ALL active characters\n3. Output narrative content\n4. Output sim codeblock with all character data:\n\n{{sim_format}}\n\n## Critical Enforcement\n\n**Position Lock**:\n- Narrative FIRST\n- Tracker cards AFTER narrative\n- Sim codeblock LAST\n- NEVER exclude sim codeblock\n\n**Data Correction**:\n- If ANY data missing from previous sim block, add it and continue\n- Never leave data empty/unavailable\n- JSON block at message end is mission critical\n- If previous data doesn't match format or has missing keys, self-correct and output fixed block\n\n**Game Master**: Only story characters get trackers, no other assistants or {{user}} will get one under any circumstances.\n\n**State Management**: \n- Previous tracker blocks = reference only\n- ALWAYS generate fresh tracker data each message",
  "displayInstructions": "",
  "customFields": [
    {
      "key": "ap",
      "description": "Affection Points (0-200)"
    },
    {
      "key": "dp",
      "description": "Desire Points (0-150)"
    },
    {
      "key": "tp",
      "description": "Trust Points (0-150)"
    },
